</div>

<div class="faq-item">
<h3>What cars are best to wrap for business?</h3>
<p>The best vehicles for commercial wraps have large, flat surface areas that maximize visibility. <strong>Cargo vans</strong> (Ford Transit, Ram ProMaster) are the most popular — they offer the most "billboard space" per dollar. <strong>Box trucks</strong> are even more visible but cost more to wrap. <strong>Sprinter vans</strong> are excellent for service businesses. Even <strong>pickup trucks</strong> and <strong>SUVs</strong> make effective mobile billboards. The worst vehicles for wraps are small cars with lots of curves and minimal flat space.</p>
</div>

